T02D2119:159a-0: @159a ` // 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpa' la //
T02D2119:159a-2: 'dod pa'i don grub dam pa ste //
T02D2119:159a-4: las bzhi'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga bstan par bya ste /
T02D2119:159a-5: de yang nub dang po lhan cig skyes pa'i bdud dang bral bar bya ba'i phyir ;
T02D2119:159a-7: de nas bar chod kyi bdud dang dbral bar bya ba'i phyir drag po'i sbyin sreg bya'o //
T02D2119:159a-8: dang po thab dang rdzas kyi mtshan nyid bstan te zhi ba la dbyibs zlum po /
T02D2119:159a-9: dpangs dang zhes du sor bzhi ba bya'o //
T02D2119:159a-10: rgyal khru gang kha dog dkar po'o //
T02D2119:159a-11: yang na chur mdzub gang dbangs su chag gang do /
T02D2119:159a-13: dkar gsum mngar gsum gu gul dkar po de rnams so //
T02D2119:159a-14: drag po la zur gsum dbangs sa sor bzhi zheng chur khru re'o //
T02D2119:159a-15: rdzas khrag dang dug dang til nag dang nyungs na
T02D2119:159a-16: ga lidg dmar nag dang rdzad rnams thams cad nag
T02D2119:159a-17: po'o // dbang la zla gam zhi ba'i phyed de kha khyer la'o //
T02D2119:159a-19: rdzas dmar po la sogs pa bya'o //
T02D2119:159a-22: mar dang nas smug po rnams so //
T02D2119:159a-23: rgyas pa la grub bzhi rtse khru gang zer /
T02D2119:159a-25: sbom phra chag gang ba me tog la sogs pa'i rdzas thams cad ser por bsag go //
T02D2119:159a-26: thun mong gi mchod pa'i rdzas rnams ni //
T02D2119:159a-27: mar dang 'bras dang sran ma dang /
T02D2119:159a-29: dus ni zhi ba la nyin phyed /
T02D2119:159a-31: drag po la nam phye ba ba lhor bltas la bya'o //
T02D2119:159a-32: dbang la nyi ma nub ka kha nub tu bltas la bya'o //
T02D2119:159a-33: rgyas pa la dus snga dro kha byang du bltas la bya'o //
T02D2119:159a-34: dgang gzar ni zhi ba la dngul /
T02D2119:159a-37: rgyas pa la gser las bya'o //
T02D2119:159a-38: de nas me lha bskyed pa ni /
T02D2119:159a-39: rang 'jam dpal du gsal ba'i thugs ka nas /
T02D2119:159a-40: h'um dang dza: 'phros pas thab kyi nang du babs /
T02D2119:159a-43: gundha zhu ba las me lha sku mdog dkar por gyur /
T02D2119:159a-45: gsus pa ldir ba tshangs pa'i skud pas brgyan pa /
T02D2119:159b-0: dza: zhu ba las yum sku @159b mdog ser mo g-yas lcags kyu g-yon phreng ba 'dzin pa'o //
T02D2119:159b-1: yab kyi g-yon ngos su 'khril bar bsgom mo //
T02D2119:159b-2: me lha'i thugs kar me'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum cig bsam /
T02D2119:159b-3: bdag gi thugs ka nas me'i dkyil 'khor la bhr'um
T02D2119:159b-4: cig 'phros de zhu ba las gzhal yas khang gdan
T02D2119:159b-6: de'i nang du lha nyi shu rdzus skyes su bsgom /
T02D2119:159b-7: rnam pa nyi shus byang chub pa gsung ngo //
T02D2119:159b-9: skad cig gcig gis rdzogs sangs rgyas //
T02D2119:159b-11: dam tshig sems dpa' bskyed pa'i rim pa'o //
T02D2119:159b-12: de nas ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs te /
T02D2119:159b-13: dad pa dang ni dam tshig g 'tshal lo //
T02D2119:159b-15: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs sems dpa' che //
T02D2119:159b-16: lha yi rgyal po bram ze yin //
T02D2119:159b-17: 'bar ba'i nang du gshegs nas kyang /
T02D2119:159b-18: sreg rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes shig / aagni dri
T02D2119:159b-19: shya aam ku sha dza: h'um bam ho: zhes gnyis
T02D2119:159b-21: de nas me lha la sreg rdzas dbul ba ni /
T02D2119:159b-22: rdzas gong ma rnams dbul lo //
T02D2119:159b-23: aom w'a g'a shva ri mum /
T02D2119:159b-24: sarba ta th'a ga ta aagni ha bya ka bya zhi ba sh'ntim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-25: rgyas pa la pushtim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-26: dbang la ba shyam ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-27: drag po la m'a ra ya phat sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-28: nyi shu rtsa gcig dbul lo //
T02D2119:159b-29: de nas me lha bstod de /
T02D2119:159b-30: tshangs pa 'jig rten mgon gyi sras /
T02D2119:159b-31: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /'jig rten yongs la bskyab pa'i phyir //
T02D2119:159b-32: thugs rje dbang gis sku sbrul ba //
T02D2119:159b-33: rig sngags 'dzin cing gsang sngags gsung //
T02D2119:159b-34: bdud rtsi bcud ldan gundhe bsnams //
T02D2119:159b-35: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pas //
T02D2119:159b-36: thugs rje'i sprul pa khyed la bstod /
T02D2119:159b-38: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha la mchod pa 'bul te /
T02D2119:159b-39: aom na ma: sa manta m'a ra ne zhi ba sh'ntim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-40: aom badzra bi dza ye zhi ba sh'antim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-41: aom badzra ma le pa sha zhi ba sh'ntim sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-42: aom badzra ma h'a ba le zhi ba sh'ntim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-43: aom ka ma ri zhi pa sh'ntim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-44: aom badzra ti ti pra be zhi ba sh'anti ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-45: rgyas pa la pushtim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-46: dbang la ba shyam ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-47: drag po la m'a ra ya phat sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-48: nyi shu rtsa gcig dbul lo //
T02D2119:159b-49: aom badzra pushpe zhi ba sh'ntim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-50: dhu pe zhi ba sh'ntim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-51: badzra a'a lo ke zhi ba sh'ntimku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:159b-52: badzra ga ndhe zhi pa sh'ntim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:160a-1: nee bi tye zhi bash'intam ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:160a-2: badra shabda zhi ba shintam ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02D2119:160a-3: bam shyam ku ru pui shtam ku ru /
T02D2119:160a-5: mchod pa'i mjug tu re re brjod do //
T02D2119:160a-6: de nas bstod pa bya ba ni /
T02D2119:160a-7: gzhon nu'i sku lus 'chad ba po //
T02D2119:160a-8: ye shes sgron mes rab brgyan cing //
T02D2119:160a-9: 'jig rten gsum gyi mun sel ba'i //
T02D2119:160a-11: nyid kyi 'dab bzang tshogs kyis ni //
T02D2119:160a-12: zla brgyas pa'ang zil gnon cing //
T02D2119:160a-13: rig pa rnam par gsal 'gyur ba //
T02D2119:160a-15: ma bgyis don gyis zur gsal ba //
T02D2119:160a-16: nor bu 'bar ba'i sku mnga' zhing //
T02D2119:160a-17: nyid ni kun du gsal ba'i sku //
T02D2119:160a-19: bdud rtsi dri zhim 'jam pa yi //
T02D2119:160a-20: yid 'ong gsum gyi sgra sgrogs la //
T02D2119:160a-21: ngam pa chos kyi rin chen mdzod //
T02D2119:160a-23: gangs kyi chu ltar gsal ba la //
T02D2119:160a-24: 'jig rten khams rnams rnam par bzhugs //
T02D2119:160a-25: nyon mongs dri ma rnam spangs pa //
T02D2119:160a-27: mche ba gtsigs shing 'jigs pa yi //
T02D2119:160a-28: 'jigs pa'i sku yi tshul gyis ni //
T02D2119:160a-29: gshin rje'i dregs pa 'joms mjad pa //
T02D2119:160a-31: ras kyi sbyan dang ma dang sa 'dra ba /
T02D2119:160a-34: shes rab ral gri mda' gzhu 'dzin //
T02D2119:160a-36: phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas la //
T02D2119:160a-37: rgya che'i spyod par bston pa //
T02D2119:160a-38: 'gro ba'i lam ni ston pa po //
T02D2119:160a-40: de nas 'dud pa nyi shus bstod do //
T02D2119:160a-41: de nas smon lam gdab ste //
T02D2119:160a-42: bar chad ma lus zhi gter sgrub pa /
T02D2119:160a-43: 'jam dpal gyi bsnyen pa gzhung bzhin bsdu ba dang //
T02D2119:160a-44: tshe dang dbang thang bskyed pa'i phyir //
T02D2119:160a-45: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub stsol //
T02D2119:160a-46: aom badzra mu: / zhes pas gshegs su gsol //
